collections.name: Dreamscapes: The Lost Realms
collections.description:
"Dreamscapes: The Lost Realms" is a collection of surreal, one-of-a-kind NFTs inspired by the mysterious and ethereal world of dreams. Each piece captures a fleeting moment from the subconscious—a place where reality bends, memories intertwine, and imagination knows no bounds.

From infinite gardens of glowing stars to celestial cities floating in the void, every artwork tells a story of wonder, longing, and exploration. Accompanied by symbolic interpretations, these NFTs invite collectors to dive into the depths of their own minds and uncover the hidden meanings behind the dreamlike visions.

This collection is not just art—it's a journey into the unknown, where every piece is a portal to a forgotten realm.
